data.description: SOLD AS-IS. Seller will do no repairs. Rare opportunity to purchase a fixer-upper in Elderwoods Townhomes.  This property sports a corner lot and has a great layout with vaulted ceilings in the spacious living and dining areas.  The functional kitchen has a full size washer-dryer hookup as well as access to the front courtyard. The large living and dining areas are separated by a beautiful brick fireplace and feature 2 large skylights and ample natural light from the back yard area.  The primary suite has been demo'd already and is ready for the next owner to finish in their preferred materials. The current primary bath features dual vanity areas and dual closets.  The guest bedroom is large and has back yard access.  The quiet townhome community is just minutes from downtown, is adjacent to the Red Bird Golf Course and is down the street from the awesome up-and-coming Redbird Mall Redevelopment.  Great opportunity here!
